tml"><ins>Charter</ins></a>和<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tag/disney/"><ins>迪士尼</ins></a>解决了自 8 月 31 日以来数百万客户无法通过其有线电视提供商观看<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tag/abc/"><ins>ABC</ins></a>和<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tag/espn/"><ins>ESPN</ins></a>等网络的纠纷。两家公司<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://thewaltdisneycompany.com/disney-charter-spectrum-agreement/"><ins>达成了一项协议</ins></a>，为 Spectrum 订户提供一些有趣的流媒体相关福利。其中包括使用 Spectrum TV Select 套餐的用户可以访问期待已久的<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/disney-is-reportedly-laying-the-groundwork-for-its-standalone-espn-streaming-service-172721356.html"><ins>独立 ESPN 流媒体服务</ins></a>（无论该服务何时推出）。</p><p>这些订户还将在未来几个月内访问由广告支持的<a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tag/disney-plus/"><ins>Disney+</ins></a>基本层，而 Spectrum TV Select Plus 客户将能够查看<a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tag/espn-plus/"><ins>ESPN+</ins></a> ，作为其计划的一部分。据<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:CNBC;elmt:;cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=34e37b9c-8975-48da-aa39-df8bcd5badc3&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=CNBC&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAWiyiUjrGKJiuWB2QSTZlIe5zo076_mYIi_Wt3ucXLvm&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2023%2F09%2F11%2Fdisney-charter-near-carriage-deal-that-would-end-cable-blackout-sources-say.html%3F__source%3Dsharebar%257Ctwitter%26par%3Dsharebar" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.cnbc.com/2023/09/11/disney-charter-near-carriage-deal-that-would-end-cable-blackout-sources-say.html?__source=sharebar%7Ctwitter&amp;par=sharebar"><em><ins>CNBC 报道</ins></em></a>，Charter 将向迪士尼支付更高的订阅费。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>在最终达成交易之前，特许客户能否访问迪士尼流媒体服务的广告支持版本似乎是两家公司之间争论的焦点。与此同时，迪士尼在 10 月份提价之前开始<a data-i13n="cpos:10;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/get-hulu--live-tv-for-50-a-month-before-the-upcoming-price-hike-kicks-in-131516358.html"><ins>以每月 50 美元的折扣价格提供三个月的</ins></a>Hulu + Live TV（通常价格为 70 美元）。</p><p> Charter 和迪士尼之间新达成的协议意味着订户再次可以访问后者的 19 个网络，包括 ABC 旗下的电视台、迪士尼频道、FX 和国家地理频道。正好赶上<em>周一橄榄球之夜</em>，全套 ESPN 网络也回归了。然而，Spectrum 订户正在失去通过有线电视服务观看 Baby TV、Disney Junior、Disney XD、Freeform、FXM、FXX、Nat Geo Wild 和 Nat Geo Mundo 的能力。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/disney-channels-are-back-on-spectrum-after-12-day-standoff-174333955.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/disney-channels-are-back-on-spectrum-after-12-day-standoff-174333955.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> dea1fe98-7563-4cdd-984e-f1592c06fb3f</guid><dc:creator>克里斯·霍尔特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Mon, 11 Sep 2023 17:43:33 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1694454214</ingested><modified> 2023-09-11T17:43:37+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Professional Services]]></category><category><![CDATA[Television]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Kris Holt]]></category><media:content height="1265" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/45ce18c0-50c8-11ee-bdd5-8c98caa12efd" width="1889"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1265" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/45ce18c0-50c8-11ee-bdd5-8c98caa12efd" width="1889"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:ide